&kp Q  &kp X       &kp C       &kp D             &kp V               &kp Z          &kp K           &kp H                &kp COMMA          &kp DOT     &kp FSLH         &kp BSLH
                               &kp LEFT_CONTROL  &mo 4               &lt 1 SPACE    &kp LEFT_SHIFT  &kp RIGHT_ALT        &sl 5
