         &kp ENTER  &kp LEFT       &kp DOWN          &kp RIGHT      &kp PAGE_UP          &kp LS(ENTER)  &kp C_VOL_UP  &kp C_VOL_DN  &kp KP_N6  &kp LS(ENTER)
&kp ESC  &kp DEL    &kp LG(LS(S))  &kp K_PLAY_PAUSE  &kp LEFT_ALT   &kp PAGE_DOWN        &kp RPAR       &kp KP_N1     &kp KP_N2     &kp KP_N3  &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &to 2
